      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction to April 21 picture caption with article about India Now, film series at Museum of Modern Art, concerns actress shown in scene from film in series</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption in The Arts last Saturday with an article about ''India Now,'' a film series at the Museum of Modern Art, included erroneous information from the museum about the actress shown in a scene from ''Dor,'' a film in the series. She was Gul Panag -- not Ayesha Takia, one of the movie's stars.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A picture caption in The Arts last Saturday with an article about ''India Now,'' a film series at the Museum of Modern Art, included erroneous information from the museum about the actress shown in a scene from ''Dor,'' a film in the series. She was Gul Panag -- not Ayesha Takia, one of the movie's stars.</p>
      </block>
